{"tid":1501853,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"各位WarGame嘅手足可唔可以唔好再攞氣槍出嚟?!","createTime":"2019-08-24T13:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T02:35:57.000Z","uid":288688,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3b0dfcdab4e73fb88e11092e20485f15514b10ee","tid":1501853,"uid":288688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:22:22.000Z","msg":"今日見到有手足帶Glock19嘅氣槍出嚟,唔該各位wargame界嘅手足可唔可以唔好再帶氣槍出嚟?我唔理你有冇改過都好, 你唔好期待6mm嘅鐵珠對班著曬甲既差佬做得到幾多傷害, 你要攞槍唔係唔得得,去攞支真槍唔該,至少你畀人射低咗嘅話,我可以幫你攞支槍射返過去, 但你得支氣槍嘅話我點幫你報仇呢? 同埋加上班差佬去遠距離冇可能分得出你攞氣槍定真槍,佢肯定攞真槍射咗你先, 大佬呀,我唔想成班手足喺自己友冇真槍嘅情況下同你一齊食.38 special同真散彈啊..... 我自己都係一個wargame友,所以真係唔該你哋唔好再攞支氣槍出嚟啦好冇? 我話知你把嘢改到可以射底膛壓嘅子彈都好啦, 只要你嗰支槍唔係正式真槍你都唔好攞出嚟啦好冇?!"},{"pid":"f8292bc99711b90ed0d4aa828038bd0c158f748d","tid":1501853,"uid":288688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:23:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5d5b35927a8447d967aeae70b8d57ce26ff67e3","tid":1501853,"uid":288688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:23:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4190f3a99966f08acac93b968d1b602cb63d0a7","tid":1501853,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:24:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed65f444a979e0282d6835a890894b85a4df43d","tid":1501853,"uid":288688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:24:40.000Z","msg":"頭先打錯咗,應該唔係19總之係glock系列啦"},{"pid":"1badb5373c6bbf63098c3cf7c1eb60081e7a5091","tid":1501853,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T13:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" c